Quickstrike:






Quickstrike turned around the instant Dark Mouse hit the floor. "Dark 
Mouse!" He quickly bent down to her. "Don't do this! Hey, get up!" He shook 
her trying to wake her. He stood up and grabbed her by the arms. He dragged 
her to the CR room, but when he got her there, he knew it was too late. He 
stared at her lifeless body. It wasn't fair. He never knew a bot he liked 
that died on him.

His optics glowed an almost expressionless glare. He slowly walked out of 
the room, into the corridor. He pressed his back against the wall and slid 
his body down into the floor. He ducked his head between his knees and made 
a strange whimpering tone.
